{"tid":1334922,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【證監會已死?】小米集團回應：之前漏報了其他客戶的小米權益 不算雷軍增持。","createTime":"2019-07-20T09:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T10:12:50.000Z","uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8068088f973617e04d219803983a36d948854cfb","tid":1334922,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"小米集團(<a href=\"http://01810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01810.HK&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=dc5695d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01810.HK</a>)  +0.110 (+1.222%)    沽空 $2.26億; 比率 41.960%   於5月27日再向主要股東ARK Trust派發獎勵股份，但事件延至7月16日才向聯交所披露。<br />\n<br />\n據披露顯示，ARK Trust獲給予股份，涉及股份數目為17.76億股，令其持股量由17.62%升至27.87%。<br />\n<br />\n在小米上市前，ARK Trust以受託人身份為創辦人及大股東雷軍成立，並以雷軍及其家族為受益人的信託持有，但上市後有其他股份獎勵計劃的受益人成為ARK Trust客戶，故ARK Trust不再只代表雷軍。而是次派發股份，集團並沒有披露受益人的最終身分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.952700/recommend-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.952700%2Frecommend-news&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=89293244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.952700/recommend-news</a><br />\n<br />\n小米集團回應：之前漏報了其他客戶的小米權益 不算雷軍增持。"},{"pid":"c9d6587c951b1d3a1b779b283f827de74e53bd43","tid":1334922,"uid":27150,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"8068088f973617e04d219803983a36d948854cfb","tid":1334922,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"小米集團(<a href=\"http://01810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01810.HK&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=dc5695d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01810.HK</a>)  +0.110 (+1.222%)    沽空 $2.26億; 比率 41.960%   於5月27日再向主要股東ARK Trust派發獎勵股份，但事件延至7月16日才向聯交所披露。<br />\n<br />\n據披露顯示，ARK Trust獲給予股份，涉及股份